thread.title: LSU fraternity's house dad dies on campus
thread.title_full: LSU fraternity's house dad dies on campus - FOX 8 WVUE New Orleans News, Weather, Sports, Social

author: WAFB Staff
title: LSU fraternity's house dad dies on campus
text:
BATON ROUGE, LA (WAFB) - The house dad for an LSU fraternity died Tuesday afternoon in the fraternity house.
LSU Police and EMS were called out to the Kappa Alpha Fraternity house around 12:17 p.m. Tuesday. LSU spokesman Ernie Ballard said they were dispatched because the 52-year-old man was unresponsive. He died before authorities arrived.
According to LSU, the East Baton Rouge Parish coroner will determine the cause of death.
Police say there are currently no signs of foul play.
